<HL>
   SEC Votes to Limit
   Money Managers'
   Soft-Dollar Deals
   ----
   By Kevin G. Salwen and James A. White
   Staff Reporters of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
07/26/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE C17
</SO>
